    <release version="1.0.0" date="2024-09-08">
      <url type="details">https://github.com/MrPiggy92/ScriptedJourneys/blob/master/changelog</url>
      <description>
          <p>First release</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Multiple Maps: Explore different environments such as dungeons, forests, and towns.</li>
            <li>Item Management: Collect and use items to overcome obstacles.</li>
            <li>Mini-bosses: Fight small bosses as you work your way up the levels.</li>
            <li>Spells: Cast powerful spells to do everything from instantly killing an enemy to teleporting through the map.</li>
